                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9777" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-1468</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">769 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">打造观众心流体验：爱奇艺植入式广告的进阶之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Creating Audience Flow Experience: The Advancing Path of iQiyi&#39;s Brand Placement</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">姚卿，向正杰，谷丰</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京科技大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京爱奇艺科技有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">文化、体育和娱乐业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">爱奇艺；植入式广告；心流体验；说服知识理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">IQiyi; Brand Placement; Flow Experience; Persuasion Knowledge Model</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">对于视频平台运营商和广告主而言，“如何实现高质量的广告植入”是一项极具挑战性的难题，为了在有效传递广告信息的同时保障观众的观看体验，各方在广告内容和表现形式方面不断探索新的可能。本案例重点讲述了爱奇艺作为长视频平台领跑者，自成立之初便致力于对广告植入策略持续优化与创新的故事。在植入内容方面，爱奇艺实现了广告线索与剧情故事的深度融合；在表现形式方面，爱奇艺开发了丰富多样的广告植入路径；在技术水平方面，爱奇艺利用人工智能匹配潜在受众完成广告精准投放。上述一系列举措帮助爱奇艺实现了从简单“硬植入”到进阶“软植入”的华丽转身，而其中成功的关键在于强化植入式广告的沉浸感以促进观众的心流体验。本案例旨在引导学生分析当前植入式广告存在的优势和局限，帮助其理解心流理论在新媒体营销过程中的实际应用，以及思考新技术、新平台的诞生对广告行业可能产生的具体影响。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">For video platform operators and advertisers, “how to achieve high-quality advertising placement” constitutes a significant and challenging dilemma. To effectively convey advertising messages while safeguarding viewer experience, stakeholders continuously explore new possibilities in advertising content and presentation formats. This case study focuses on iQiyi, a leading long-form video platform, detailing its story of persistent optimization and innovation in advertising placement strategies since its inception. In terms of placement content, iQiyi has achieved deep integration of advertising cues with narrative storylines. Regarding presentation formats, iQiyi has developed a diverse array of advertising placement pathways. On the technological front, iQiyi utilizes artificial intelligence to match potential audiences and execute precision-targeted advertising delivery. This series of initiatives facilitated iQiyi’s marked transformation from simplistic “hard placements” to sophisticated “soft placements”. The critical success factor lies in enhancing the immersive quality of embedded advertising to foster viewers’ flow experiences. This case study aims to guide students in analyzing the inherent advantages and limitations of contemporary embedded advertising; facilitate their understanding of the practical application of flow theory within new media marketing processes; and encourage critical reflection on the potential concrete impacts of emerging technologies and platforms on the advertising industry.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《网络营销》、《新媒体营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">植入式广告；说服知识理论；心流理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-09</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
